Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.82,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}My first guest is a great actress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:06.19,EN,,0,0,0,,and you can see her as wonder woman in the new movie {\i1}Wonder Woman 1984{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.67,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s in select theatres and IMAX on Christmas Day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.89,EN,,0,0,0,,and will also be available on the same day on HBO Max
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:15.13,EN,,0,40,0,,Here is Gal Gadot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.66,EN,,0,0,0,,Gal! My goodness is so good to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.77,EN,,0,0,0,,We’re hugging you from here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.13,EN,,0,0,0,,I’m hugging you from here, too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, pal, it’s so great to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:25.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming back to our show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:29.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Can you believe {\i1}Wonder Woman 1984{\i0} is finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.14,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s here, it’s finally happening
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:32.39,EN,,0,0,0,,I can and I can’t at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.64,EN,,0,0,0,,We’ve been waiting for such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.82,EN,,0,0,0,,for to be able to share this with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.84,EN,,0,0,0,,and now is the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:42.08,EN,,0,0,0,,And it’s so surreal that we’ve just releasing the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:45.29,EN,,0,0,0,,and I don’t get to see you like everything is virtual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.73,EN,,0,0,0,,The world had gone crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.77,EN_UP,,0,0,0,,I know, but it’s a great...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:48.43,EN,,0,0,0,,And I’m supper excited
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:53.03,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to say that this movie has more action than the first one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.54,EN,,0,0,0,,Did you know that going into it that you’re gonna be like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.26,EN,,0,0,0,,I’m going to be exhausted in this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did. Patty made a big point about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:04.62,EN,,0,0,0,,wanting to have minimum account of CGI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.57,EN,,0,0,0,,which is great and I love this idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:10.39,EN,,0,0,0,,I just didn’t really understood what it meant for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:13.81,EN,,0,0,0,,and what it did mean was that we just, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:18.09,EN,,0,0,0,,both Kristen, too, and I had to do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.89,EN,,0,0,0,,So much stunt work by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to show you one thing that I noticed when I watched it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.27,EN,,0,0,0,,There was one kick that you did that I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.32,EN_UP,,0,0,0,,Oh that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.32,EN,,0,0,0,,your body was like, you were parallel, like it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.21,EN,,0,0,0,,The front kick, the front kick lay out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.12,EN,,0,0,0,,The front kick lay out is what it’s called?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:37.88,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s horizontal and…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.21,EN,,0,0,0,,Were you on wires?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.51,EN,,0,0,0,,That was assisted majorly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:45.38,EN,,0,0,0,,and that was also my stunt girl who’s like, amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.49,EN,,0,0,0,,I wanted, cause I asked the studio for this clip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.47,EN,,0,0,0,,cause I just wanted to watch it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:49.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I watch this clip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Dave, could we watch this? - Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let’s watch it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.75,EN,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Stop right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.91,EN,,0,0,0,,Look at that! Look at that! Perfection!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.35,EN,,0,0,0,,That is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.33,EN,,0,0,0,,And holding the gun and the lasso
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.89,EN,,0,0,0,,And the lasso. I mean, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.34,EN,,0,0,0,,That’s the poster right there. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.16,EN,,0,0,0,,I also remember seeing something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:16.15,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought it was you flying in the invisible jet or something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.52,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a spoiler or something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.24,EN,,0,0,0,,cause it looked like you were sitting in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.35,EN,,0,0,0,,I know, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:29.42,EN,,0,0,0,,That was not the invisible jet, that was me being a major pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.32,EN,,0,0,0,,We shut down Penn Avenue in Washington D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:37.94,EN,,0,0,0,,for a few days and I had to do like this intense running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:43.20,EN,,0,0,0,,and I was wired, like from here and from here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.55,EN,,0,0,0,,and they pulled me as the same speed as Usain Bolt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.67,EN,,0,0,0,,ran when he won one of his medals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.79,EN,,0,0,0,,He’s the fastest man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. So we had to, so that’s what we did
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.73,EN,,0,0,0,,cause you’re actually running, and the wires are pulling you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:05.64,EN,,0,0,0,,But the craziest thing is you gonna make sure that like every time, every stride
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.00,EN,,0,0,0,,you hit the floor so it does look like you’re running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:14.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I auditioned, and yeah, they actually didn’t even call me back at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.12,EN,,0,0,0,,but whatever, it’s a little rude, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.42,EN,,0,0,0,,I will say our pal Kristen Wiig crushes it in this movie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.95,EN,,0,0,0,,She’s also in the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:25.21,EN,,0,0,0,,We actually adore each other so much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.12,EN,,0,0,0,,We had a crazy instant connection, it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:33.24,EN,,0,0,0,,She, because the movie was so laborious and they were so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.45,EN,,0,0,0,,It was very long and we shot the movie for eight months
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:42.42,EN,,0,0,0,,in five different locations, and it was just, like super physical as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.48,EN,,0,0,0,,The fact that she was there with me doing these crazy things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:50.57,EN,,0,0,0,,but also, like, being her, she’s like the most
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.78,EN,,0,0,0,,She's so, you know, but she’s like I’ll tell everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:57.35,EN,,0,0,0,,Guys you’re missing on not knowing Kristen Wiig,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:03.03,EN,,0,0,0,,She’s like fun and funny, and open, like, she made this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:07.36,EN,,0,0,0,,so, so delightful for me, and I’m super grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:12.00,EN,,0,0,0,,We know that you guys became fast friends and really good friends on the set
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.63,EN,,0,0,0,,and this is really very very cool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.60,EN,,0,0,0,,You guys sent us one of your music videos
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.40,EN,,0,0,0,,You made a music video together, it’s very low budget
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:23.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Here is an exclusive world premiere of Gal Gadot and Kristen Wiig’s video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:24.54,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.36,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ Gal and Kristen having fun! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.49,EN,,790,0,8,,♪ We are Gal and Kristen and we're having fun ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.37,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ Sometimes we run, jump in the air ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:42.36,EN,,850,0,8,,♪ Sometimes we stare and then flip our hair ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.33,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ We’re friends, and we like science ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.23,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ We feel comfortable in total silence ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.14,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ Come on everybody, dancing in the sun ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.94,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ Cause we’re Gal and Krissy ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.25,EN,,700,0,8,,♪ And we’re having fun! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.21,EN,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.41,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s a fake applause at the end, and the kids
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.95,EN,,0,0,0,,It is honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.95,EN_UP,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.92,EN,,0,0,0,,And we are having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.47,EN,,0,0,0,,Gal and Krissy, and we are having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.95,EN,,0,0,0,,Dude, that’s catchy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.51,EN,,0,0,0,,The claps and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.13,EN,,0,0,0,,That was the funniest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.35,EN,,0,0,0,,Can you tell everyone what’s going on in {\i1}Wonder Woman 1984{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:31.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. Wow, where do I begin without giving away too many spoilers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.59,EN,,0,0,0,,What I can tell you is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:36.23,EN,,0,0,0,,it’s the most ambitious movie I’ve ever got to make
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.89,EN,,0,0,0,,As far as the story telling we have four different storylines
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.23,EN,,0,0,0,,As far as the action goes, like we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.29,EN,,0,0,0,,There’s so much action for real
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:49.12,EN,,0,0,0,,As for as location and the scope, it’s huge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.70,EN,,0,0,0,,And I’m very, very excited to share it with everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.47,EN,,0,0,0,,And I hope that people are going to enjoy it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.63,EN,,0,0,0,,and have a wonderful two and a half hours watching it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.63,EN,,0,0,0,,We need it right now more than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.78,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to show everyone a clip from the film
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.78,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Here is Gal Gadot in {\i1}Wonder Woman 1984{\i0}, Take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, aren’t you resourceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.08,EN,,0,0,0,,No, I don’t think so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Remove this woman, please. Permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.07,EN,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.51,EN,,0,0,0,,I don’t know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:53.04,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}{\i1}Wonder Woman 1984{\i0} will be in select theaters and IMAX on Christmas Day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.13,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}and will be available the same day on HBO max
Comment: 1,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.96,CN,,0,0,0,,--------------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.82,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}我的第一位嘉宾是位杰出的女演员
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.82,0:00:06.19,CN,,0,0,0,,她在新的电影《神奇女侠1984》中扮演神奇女侠
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.67,CN,,0,0,0,,电影会在圣诞节那天在精选剧院和IMAX上映
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.89,CN,,0,0,0,,并且也将于当天在HBO Max上线
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.89,0:00:15.13,CN,,0,0,0,,这是盖尔·加朵！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.66,CN,,0,0,0,,盖尔！啊这简直太好了…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.77,CN,,0,0,0,,我们从这里拥抱你
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.13,CN,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.73,CN,,0,0,0,,噢，见到你可真太高兴了，朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.73,0:00:25.14,CN,,0,0,0,,感谢你回到我们的节目
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.57,0:00:29.28,CN,,0,0,0,,你敢相信《神奇女侠1984》终于要上映了？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.14,CN,,0,0,0,,它就在这里，正在发生
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.14,0:00:32.39,CN,,0,0,0,,我可以想象，但我不能同时和你一起见证这一切
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.64,CN,,0,0,0,,我们已经等了太久
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.82,CN,,0,0,0,,终于可以和全世界分享它了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.84,CN,,0,0,0,,现在这一刻到来了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.84,0:00:42.08,CN,,0,0,0,,我们要发布电影了，这感觉太离谱了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.08,0:00:45.29,CN,,0,0,0,,就像我现在没法看到真实的你，一切都是虚拟的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.73,CN,,0,0,0,,这个世界太疯狂了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.77,CN_UP,,0,0,0,,我明白，但是这很棒…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.73,0:00:48.43,CN,,0,0,0,,我现在非常兴奋
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.06,0:00:53.03,CN,,0,0,0,,我想说这部电影比起第一部电影多了更多的战斗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.54,CN,,0,0,0,,你知道当你扮演这个角色的时候会像
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.26,CN,,0,0,0,,我要为此精疲力尽这样？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.02,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，的确如此。帕蒂提到了一个重要的问题
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.02,0:01:04.62,CN,,0,0,0,,是关于想要最少的CGI（电脑三维动画）
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.57,CN,,0,0,0,,这很棒，我很支持这样做
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.57,0:01:10.39,CN,,0,0,0,,我只是没有真正明白这对我意味着什么
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.39,0:01:13.81,CN,,0,0,0,,它的意思是我们只能，你知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.81,0:01:18.09,CN,,0,0,0,,克里斯汀和我都必须做很多事情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.89,CN,,0,0,0,,需要我们自己做很多特技
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我想给你看一个东西，这是我在观看的时候注意到的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.27,CN,,0,0,0,,我要说的是你踢过的一脚…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.32,CN_UP,,0,0,0,,哦这可真是
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.32,CN,,0,0,0,,你的身体就像是，你是完全平行的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.21,CN,,0,0,0,,一个前踢，前面的脚踢出来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.12,CN,,0,0,0,,所谓的前踢是指？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.12,0:01:37.88,CN,,0,0,0,,这是水平的…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.21,CN,,0,0,0,,你在威亚上吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.51,CN,,0,0,0,,那主要是协助我的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.51,0:01:45.38,CN,,0,0,0,,那也是我的特技动作，真的太神奇了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.49,CN,,0,0,0,,我问演播室要了这个剪辑片段
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.47,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我只是想要看它
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.47,0:01:49.72,CN,,0,0,0,,你介意我看这个前踢吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.98,CN,,0,0,0,,戴夫，我们可以看一下吗？-当然
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.14,CN,,0,0,0,,好，让我们来看一下
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.75,CN,,0,0,0,,看这个动作！停，就这儿！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.91,CN,,0,0,0,,看那个！看那个! 完美！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.35,CN,,0,0,0,,这太难以置信了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.33,CN,,0,0,0,,同时还拿着枪和套索
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.89,CN,,0,0,0,,还有套索。我的意思是，看看那个
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.34,CN,,0,0,0,,这一刻就像海报一样。来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.16,CN,,0,0,0,,我记得好像看到过什么
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.16,0:02:16.15,CN,,0,0,0,,我记得是你坐隐形喷气式飞机或其他什么东西飞翔
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.52,CN,,0,0,0,,好像是流出的剧透照片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.24,CN,,0,0,0,,因为看起来你好像坐在大街上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.35,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道的我明白
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.97,0:02:29.42,CN,,0,0,0,,那不是隐形的喷气机，那让我感到非常痛苦
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.32,CN,,0,0,0,,我们封锁了华盛顿特区的宾夕法尼亚大道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.32,0:02:37.94,CN,,0,0,0,,几天了，我不得不像这样如此激烈的奔跑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.17,0:02:43.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我被威亚固定了，从这里到这里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.55,CN,,0,0,0,,他们拉我让我以与博尔特比赛获胜时相同的速度奔跑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.67,CN,,0,0,0,,当他赢得他的勋章之一的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.79,CN,,0,0,0,,他是全世界跑得最快的男人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.72,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，我知道。因此我们不得不，这就是我们所做的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.86,CN,,0,0,0,,噢，因此你需要
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.73,CN,,0,0,0,,所以当威亚拉你的时候你实际上正在跑步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.73,0:03:05.64,CN,,0,0,0,,但最疯狂的是你必须确保每一步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.00,CN,,0,0,0,,你都踩到地上，所以他看起来就像你真的在跑步一样
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.13,0:03:14.08,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，我也试镜了，是的，我没…他们甚至没打电话给我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.12,CN,,0,0,0,,但无所谓了，好像有点粗鲁，但…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.42,CN,,0,0,0,,我会说我们的朋友克里斯汀•威格在这部电影里征服了它
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.95,CN,,0,0,0,,她也在这部电影里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.95,0:03:25.21,CN,,0,0,0,,实际上我们非常敬佩彼此
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.12,CN,,0,0,0,,我们有一个非常疯狂的密切的联系，这就像她
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.12,0:03:33.24,CN,,0,0,0,,因为电影的拍摄是如此的艰苦，他们是如此的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.45,CN,,0,0,0,,这太久了，这部电影我们拍了八个月
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.45,0:03:42.42,CN,,0,0,0,,在五个不同的地方，这就像，生理上的亲密
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.48,CN,,0,0,0,,她和我一起做这些疯狂的事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.48,0:03:50.57,CN,,0,0,0,,但是，作为她，她最喜欢…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.78,CN,,0,0,0,,你知道，但她就像，我会告诉其他所有人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.78,0:03:57.35,CN,,0,0,0,,那些不了解克里斯汀·威格的人，你们都错过了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.81,0:04:03.03,CN,,0,0,0,,她有趣，搞笑，开明，她让我有这样的经历
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.03,0:04:07.36,CN,,0,0,0,,所以，我很高兴，我非常感激
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.55,0:04:12.00,CN,,0,0,0,,我们知道你们在片场上很快成为了好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.63,CN,,0,0,0,,这真的很酷
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.60,CN,,0,0,0,,你们给我们发了一个音乐录影带
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.40,CN,,0,0,0,,你们一起拍了一段音乐视频，据说这视频的制作成本很低
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.90,0:04:23.94,CN,,0,0,0,,这是盖尔·加朵和克里斯汀·威格视频的独家世界首映
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.94,0:04:24.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}来让我们看看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.36,CN,,0,730,8,,{\fs50}盖尔和克里斯汀，很开心！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.49,CN,,0,950,8,,{\fs50}我们是盖尔和克里斯汀，我们很开心
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.37,CN,,0,800,8,,{\fs50}有时我们跑，在空中跳跃
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.37,0:04:42.36,CN,,0,900,8,,{\fs50}有时我们盯着看，然后撩起我们的头发
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.33,CN,,0,830,8,,{\fs50}我们是朋友，我们喜欢科学
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.23,CN,,0,830,8,,{\fs50}我们在安静的时刻感到舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.14,CN,,0,830,8,,{\fs50}拜托，各位，在阳光下跳舞
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.94,CN,,0,830,8,,{\fs50}因为我们是盖尔和克丽丝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.25,CN,,0,830,8,,{\fs50}我们很开心！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.21,CN,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.41,CN,,0,0,0,,最后是虚拟的掌声，和孩子们
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.95,CN,,0,0,0,,老实说
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.95,CN_UP,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.92,CN,,0,0,0,,我们很开心！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.47,CN,,0,0,0,,盖尔和克里斯，我们很开心！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.95,CN,,0,0,0,,伙计，这很吸引人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.51,CN,,0,0,0,,拍手和这一切
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.13,CN,,0,0,0,,这真的是最有趣的事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.35,CN,,0,0,0,,你能告诉大家《神奇女侠1984》里都发生了什么吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.51,0:05:31.10,CN,,0,0,0,,哦，天哪。 哇，我从哪里开始不会给太多的剧透？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.59,CN,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.59,0:05:36.23,CN,,0,0,0,,这是我拍过的最雄心勃勃的电影
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.89,CN,,0,0,0,,就故事情节而言，我们有四条不同的故事线
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.23,CN,,0,0,0,,就战斗而言，就像我们之前谈到的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.29,CN,,0,0,0,,里面有很多真实的战斗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.29,0:05:49.12,CN,,0,0,0,,至于地点和范围，它是庞大的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.70,CN,,0,0,0,,我非常，非常兴奋能和大家分享这一切
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.47,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望人们会喜欢这部电影
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.63,CN,,0,0,0,,这将会是精彩的两个半小时
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.63,CN,,0,0,0,,我们现在比以前更需要它
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.78,CN,,0,0,0,,我想给大家看一段电影剪辑的片段
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.78,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}这里是盖尔加朵在《神奇女侠1984》，来看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.72,CN,,0,0,59,,好吧，你不是足智多谋的吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.40,CN,,0,0,59,,跟我来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.08,CN,,0,0,59,,不，我不这么认为
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.00,CN,,0,0,59,,让这个女人消失，永远的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.07,CN,,0,0,59,,你还好吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.51,CN,,0,0,59,,我不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.75,0:06:53.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}《神奇女侠1984》将在圣诞节上映
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}并将在同一天在HBOmax上线
